// esteem-logo.js — animated ESTEEM center logo (MyST anywidget)
//
// The static artwork is the lab's REAL vector logo (SLAC ESTEEM, logo03.pdf),
// converted to SVG paths and inlined below — so the wordmark, tagline, chip and
// circuit are pixel-faithful and fully scalable. The text is left flat.
//
// Animation (loops ~3.6s, v1 of the motion):
//   1. the circuit's terminal circles blink, then
//   2. a pulse of light sweeps inward along the traces and converges on the E.
//
// The inward pulse is done with a constant-width ring mask centered on the E
// whose radius contracts; a bright recolored copy of the circuit is revealed
// only inside that ring, so the glow appears to flow along the traces toward
// the E without needing each trace digitized individually.
//
// Light/dark aware (recolors the near-black ink for dark backgrounds) and
// respects prefers-reduced-motion (falls back to the flat static logo).
//
// Tunables via model.get(): color_pulse, color_text_dark, color_ink_dark,
// animate (false → static), max_width.

